Mr. Lorenzo A. BetinoSpecial Advisor, StarVest Partners LLCNew York, NYOver the last seven years he has been a managing member of StarVest, a firm focused on investing in high-growth technology-based businesses. Earlier he was a partner and managing director of Warburg Pincus.2015 First QuarterAdded to: TD Ameritrade Holding Corp. - Omaha, NETD Ameritrade provides technology-based financial services. Revenues are $3 billion.















 















 











