Insider Activity


Individual




Lorenzo A. Bettino



Mr. Lorenzo A. Bettino is Independent Director at TD Ameritrade Holding Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at TD Ameritrade Holding Corp.
Mr. Bettino also served on the board at Proxim Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from Rensselaer Polytechnic Institute and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



